<pre>
<strong>Input:</strong>
words = [&quot;What&quot;,&quot;must&quot;,&quot;be&quot;,&quot;acknowledgment&quot;,&quot;shall&quot;,&quot;be&quot;]
maxWidth = 16
<strong>Output:</strong>
[
