	<li>Each <code>grid[i][j]</code> is an integer in the set <code>{-1, 0, 1}</code>.</li>
	<li>It is guaranteed that grid[0][0] and grid[N-1][N-1] are not -1.</li>
	<li>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	</li>
</ul>
', 'class Solution:
