11111
11111
1<b>1</b>111
<b>111</b>11
1<b>1</b>011
In the above grid, the largest plus sign can only be order 2.  One of them is marked in bold.
</pre></p>

<p><b>Example 2:</b><br /><pre>
<b>Input:</b> N = 2, mines = []
