So we will choose the smallest K, which is 0.
</pre>

<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><code>A</code>&nbsp;will have&nbsp;length at most <code>20000</code>.</li>
	<li><code>A[i]</code> will be in the range <code>[0, A.length]</code>.</li>
</ul>
', 'class Solution:
