A = [1, 3, 5, 7] and B = [1, 2, 3, 4]
which are both strictly increasing.
</pre>

<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><code>A, B</code> are arrays with the same length, and that length will be in the range <code>[1, 1000]</code>.</li>
