<strong>Output: </strong>[123,456,579]
</pre>

<p><strong>Example 2:</strong></p>

<pre>
<strong>Input: </strong>&quot;11235813&quot;
<strong>Output: </strong>[1,1,2,3,5,8,13]
</pre>

<p><strong>Example 3:</strong></p>

<pre>
<strong>Input: </strong>&quot;112358130&quot;
