</pre>

<p><strong>Example 4:</strong></p>

<pre>
<strong>Input: </strong>&quot;0123&quot;
<strong>Output: </strong>[]
<strong>Explanation: </strong>Leading zeroes are not allowed, so &quot;01&quot;, &quot;2&quot;, &quot;3&quot; is not valid.
