<p><strong>Example 5:</strong></p>

<pre>
<strong>Input: </strong>&quot;1101111&quot;
<strong>Output: </strong>[110, 1, 111]
<strong>Explanation: </strong>The output [11, 0, 11, 11] would also be accepted.
</pre>

<p><strong>Note: </strong></p>

<ol>
