</div>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>

<ol>
	<li><code>3 &lt;= A.length &lt;= 30000</code></li>
	<li><code>A[i] == 0</code>&nbsp;or <code>A[i] == 1</code></li>
</ol>

<div>
