<p>For example, if we have an array <code>A = [&quot;babca&quot;,&quot;bbazb&quot;]</code> and deletion indices <code>{0, 1, 4}</code>, then the final array after deletions is <code>[&quot;bc&quot;,&quot;az&quot;]</code>.</p>

