<div>
<p><strong>Example 3:</strong></p>

<pre>
<strong>Input: </strong><span id="example-input-3-1">[&quot;a==b&quot;,&quot;b==c&quot;,&quot;a==c&quot;]</span>
<strong>Output: </strong><span id="example-output-3">true</span>
