<strong>Output: </strong><span id="example-output-4">false</span>
</pre>

<div>
<p><strong>Example 5:</strong></p>

<pre>
<strong>Input: </strong><span id="example-input-5-1">[&quot;c==c&quot;,&quot;b==d&quot;,&quot;x!=z&quot;]</span>
