<strong>Output: </strong><span id="example-output-2">-1</span>
<strong>Explanation:</strong>&nbsp;No matter how we flip subarrays of size 2, we can&#39;t make the array become [1,1,1].
</pre>

<div>
<p><strong>Example 3:</strong></p>

<pre>
