Flip A[5],A[6],A[7]:&nbsp;A becomes [1,1,1,1,1,1,1,1]
</pre>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div>

<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>

<ol>
	<li><code>1 &lt;= A.length &lt;=&nbsp;30000</code></li>
	<li><code>1 &lt;= K &lt;= A.length</code></li>
</ol>', 'class Solution:
